en.name: EVO Oil Organic ICEA
en.description: ICEA certifies agricultural products, processed agri-food products, feed and pet food, aquaculture products, algae and microalgae (spirulina), yeasts. It guarantees the conformity of the productions obtained with organic methods at all stages of the production chain, from the field to the table, in compliance with European Union regulations
